spec_data.Name: rubygem-parseconfig
spec_data.Description:
ParseConfig provides simple parsing of standard configuration files in the
form of 'param = value'.  It also supports nested [group] sections.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 05:13:03 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Config File Parser for Standard Unix/Linux Type Config Files
